sequenceDiagram
  participant U as user
  participant CLI as Productized CLI
  participant CFG as Config/Profile
  participant EXT as Extension Runtime
  participant PR as Provider Resolver
  participant CAP as Capability Discovery
  participant RT as Agent Runtime
  participant OUT as Output Contract

  U->>CLI: --profile code Fix test failure
  CLI->>CFG: Parse configuration and profile
  CFG-->>CLI: policy/tools/context/provider/output
  CLI->>EXT: Load trusted extension
  EXT-->>CAP: Contribution candidate capabilities
  CLI->>PR: Choose a provider that meets your capabilities
  PR-->>RT: provider adapter + model event contract
  CLI->>CAP: Calculate visible set in this round
  CAP-->>RT: Visible tools and skill index
  RT->>RT: loop / tool intent / observation
  RT-->>OUT: structured events
  OUT-->>U: TTY Rendering and final results
